  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in monitoring and managing the day-to-day operations of project</li>\n  <li>Liaise with subcontractors, surveyors and site supervisors/foremen to make sure that works are carried out in time and  smoothly on site</li>\n  <li>Attend regular meetings with owner/client/contractors/sub-contractors on the project related matters</li>\n  <li>Carry out site inspection and ensure that the works were executed to the required quality standards</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent as recognized by PE board</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years working experience in Construction industry</li>\n  <li>Independent with good communication skills</li>\n  <li>A team player with positive working attitude</li>\n  <li>Highly driven and motivated</li>\n  <li>Able to work under pressure</li>\n  <li>Certificate in WSQ: Manage Work-At-Height, WSQ: Supervise Construction Work for Workplace Safety and Health etc</li>\n</ul>",
